<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" id="mainHtml" data-bs-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - VitalConnect</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100 bg-body">
    <header class="sticky-top mt-3">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-body-tertiary shadow-sm rounded-4 border px-3">
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold d-flex align-items-center text-info" asp-page="/Index">
                        <i class="bi bi-activity me-2"></i> VitalConnect
                    </a>

                    <button class="navbar-toggler border-0" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navVital">
                        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                    </button>

                    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navVital">
                        <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0 gap-1">

                            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle fw-medium" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <i class="bi bi-people me-1"></i> Pacientes
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu shadow border-0 rounded-3 mt-2">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Paciente/Paciente">Lista de Pacientes</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Paciente/RegistroPaciente">Registrar Paciente</a></li>
                                    <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Paciente/Historial">Consultar Historial Clínico</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Paciente/Recetas">Ver Recetas Médicas</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>

                            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle fw-medium" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar-check me-1"></i> Citas
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu shadow border-0 rounded-3 mt-2">
                                    <li><h6 class="dropdown-header">Para Pacientes</h6></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Paciente/ReservarCita">Reservar Cita</a></li>
                                    <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                    <li><h6 class="dropdown-header">Para Staff Médico</h6></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Citas/Agenda">Consultar Agenda Diaria</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Citas/Gestion">Gestión General de Citas</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>

                            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle fw-medium" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <i class="bi bi-clipboard2-pulse me-1"></i> Atención
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu shadow border-0 rounded-3 mt-2">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Atenciones/Atencion">Fichas de Atención</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Atenciones/RegistrarAtencion">Registrar Atención/Receta</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>

                            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle fw-medium" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <i class="bi bi-capsule me-1"></i> Farmacia
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu shadow border-0 rounded-3 mt-2">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Medicamento/Medicamento">Inventario de Medicamentos</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Medicamento/Agregar">Agregar Medicamento</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>

                            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle fw-medium" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <i class="bi bi-person-badge me-1"></i> Personal
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu shadow border-0 rounded-3 mt-2">
                                    <li><h6 class="dropdown-header">Profesionales</h6></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Lista">Directorio Médico</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/CrearProfesional">Registrar Médico</a></li>
                                    <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                    <li><h6 class="dropdown-header">Asistentes</h6></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Asistente/Asistente">Gestión de Asistentes</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Asistente/Registrar">Registrar Asistente</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary rounded-circle p-2" onclick="toggleTheme()" type="button">
                                <i class="bi bi-sun-fill d-none-dark"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-moon-stars-fill d-none-light"></i>
                            </button>

                            <div class="dropdown">
                                <a href="#" class="d-block link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Zenon&background=0dcaf0&color=fff" width="35" height="35" class="rounded-circle border">
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end shadow border-0 mt-2 rounded-3">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Profesional">Mi Perfil Profesional</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Profesional/Registro">Configuración de Cuenta</a></li>
                                    <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item text-danger" href="#">Cerrar Sesión</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <main role="main">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-auto py-5 bg-body-tertiary border-top">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row gy-4 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-4 text-center text-md-start">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-md-start mb-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-activity text-info fs-4 me-2"></i>
                        <span class="fw-bold fs-5 text-body">VitalConnect</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-body-secondary mb-0">
                        Materia: Desarrollo de Sistemas<br>
                        VitalConnect &copy; 2026
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                    <a href="https://github.com/Rynhoz/VitalConnect" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-secondary rounded-pill px-4 py-2 btn-sm shadow-sm transition-hover">
                        <i class="bi bi-github me-2"></i>Repositorio del Proyecto
                    </a>
                    <div class="mt-2 text-body-tertiary" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">
                        Acceso abierto para revisión de código
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 text-center text-md-end">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center justify-content-md-end gap-3 small">
                        <a href="#" class="text-body-secondary text-decoration-none">Documentación</a>
                        <a href="#" class="text-body-secondary text-decoration-none">Soporte</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mt-4 pt-3 border-top">
                <div class="col-12 text-center">
                    <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0" style="font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                        <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
                        <strong>VERSIÓN DEMO:</strong> Proyecto académico con fines educativos. Esta es la base inicial del sistema, no apta para uso médico real.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <style>
        .transition-hover:hover {
            background-color: var(--bs-secondary-bg);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
    </style>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
</body>
</html>